headline: URBN Q4 Earnings & Sales Beat Estimates on Strong Brand Momentum

headline: How Investors Are Reacting To Deckers Outdoor (DECK) Surprising Q3 Beat And Resilient Margins
summary: In late January 2026, Deckers Outdoor reported Q3 2026 results with revenue and adjusted earnings per share exceeding Wall Street expectations, while maintaining durable margins and solid cash generation despite broader macroeconomic skepticism.
